          <me>
            n = \left( {a_k  \times 10^k } \right) + \left( {a_{k - 1}  \times 10^{k - 1} } 
            \right) +  \cdots  + \left( {a_1  \times 10^1 } \right) + \left( {a_0  \times 10^0 } \right)
          </me>,
          then <m>s( n ) = a_k  + a_{k - 1}  +  \cdots  + a_1  + a_0</m>.
          Use the result in <xref ref="exer_poweroftenmod3"/> to help prove each of the following:
        </p>
